{"tid":547835,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那官媒籲國民「不要動輒患上迫害妄想症」批支那遊客大鬧外國機場","createTime":"2018-02-02T01:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T11:48:08.000Z","uid":6604,"like":74,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"e4acced6be34366d838c2d3e186dffdfa8df7e5e","tid":547835,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:24:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180201/s00004/1517473215687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180201%2Fs00004%2F1517473215687&d=UJC4Fz9%2FzbY8epcqJ3oI0LZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=e2dfb89e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180201%2Fs00004%2F1517473215687&h=9b5ef3b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180201/s00004/1517473215687</a><br />\n<br />\n近日接連發生支那旅客在外國機場鬧事，結果要當地支那大使館派員善後。《人民日報》旗下海外網一個專欄，星期三晚刊文痛批國民醜態，認為有些人動不動就呼喚祖國幫忙，說是「社會巨嬰」也不為過，呼籲民眾不要在海外自導自演《戰狼》續集。<br />\n<br />\n電影《戰狼2》去年在支那上映，掀起一陣愛國熱潮。其中一句台詞曰：「在你身後有一個強大的祖國。」支那遊客大鬧外國機場時，果然也沒有忘記「強大的祖國」，驚動當地使館出面處理。文章作者舉出最近兩個例子，說明內地遊客已經習慣「動不動就向支那大使館尋求幫助」。<br />\n<br />\n上月24日，日本成田機場有百多名支那旅客不滿班機延誤，與工作人員和警察推撞、唱國歌抗議，要支那駐日使館出面調停。28日，網上流傳影片實錄一批支那旅客在伊朗德黑蘭機場不斷高呼「支那」，惹人側目。當地大使館通報，機場因為暴雪而關閉，使館方面得悉一批支那旅客情緒不穩，派人冒雪趕抵機場協調和安排住宿，眾人因而情緒激動高呼國名。<br />\n<br />\n「在和平的環境下，支那遊客在機場遭遇的一點意外，風險完全可控。無論天氣原因還是機場突發狀況，遊客透過正常管道，遵守所在國的規則，都可以維權。」文章寫道，人們看着一些人在外地機場唱國歌抗議，絕不讓人感到強大祖國的榮耀，反而是「<span style=\"color: red;\">被庸俗民族主義綁架的羞辱</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n作者提醒民眾不要動輒患上受迫害妄想症，稍有不如意就覺得別人歧視支那人：「和平年代，支那遊客就不要動不動在海外自導自演『戰狼』續集，這是對愛國主義的扭曲。在愛國之前，請先學會愛自己。」"},{"pid":"517291ee05e92007f32ffd40a7a5acdd0bbc2cc1","tid":547835,"uid":53687,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:28:38.000Z","msg":"你沒有黨了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8e8494f3086d7fade98b3637556ca911a5f9dd","tid":547835,"uid":57376,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:30:17.000Z","msg":"無事就叫你愛黨<br />\n出事就叫你自己擋<br />\n<br />\n中共好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92610d3f7ed2861374561ed0ed1efcf79c9ac172","tid":547835,"uid":53498,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:31:49.000Z","msg":"屌！咁愛唔愛呀？麻撚煩"},{"pid":"0e1d8c34c4c9878766672ac220b297f0220e6c4f","tid":547835,"uid":35430,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:47:25.000Z","msg":"百姓：想當年八國聯軍乜乜乜&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n黨：冇d咁嘅事"},{"pid":"fdc321906ba171962a623362cf7161c6d73f9bf1","tid":547835,"uid":35430,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:48:20.000Z","msg":"被迫害妄想好似係黨恩賜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24c6084a8011b119d9f0ec9815069dbebdbf105","tid":547835,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名睇五毛點定義"},{"pid":"aea269b9929cc371cde236f1a473bed290a2ae38","tid":547835,"uid":6124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd1a1d2fee781c140ae432129494c9829ffec28","tid":547835,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e24c6084a8011b119d9f0ec9815069dbebdbf105","tid":547835,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T01:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" cla